snippet: A charge of deadly conduct was dropped Tuesday against one of the men initially charged in a weekend house party in suburban Houston that left two teenagers dead.
abstract: Charge of deadly conduct is dropped against one of two suspects initially charged in fatal shooting that left two teens dead at house party in Houston suburb Cypress.
lead_paragraph: A charge of deadly conduct was dropped Tuesday against one of the men initially charged in a weekend house party in suburban Houston that left two teenagers dead.

headline.main: Texas: Charge Dropped Against One Shooting Suspect
